# These are important to set up on your side. An example file has been added for reference.
**/.env

# The README has detailed setup instructions for all three folders below.
**/cred/
**/data/
**/models/

# Virtual environment and cache files — no manual setup needed.
**/.venv/
**/__pycache__/

# Log and test files — generated at runtime, no action needed.
**/result.txt
**/test/
**/dummy.txt
**/log_details.txt
**/checkpoint_text_dump.txt

# Created at runtime by setup.py and the Chainlit framework — safe to ignore.
*.egg-info/
.chainlit/
**/chainlit.md